  "texts": [
    "The texts extracted from Kickstarter pages were found to contain a lot of noise, i.e., extraneous material unrelated to the description of the campaigns, such as boilerplate text (e.g., elements of website navigation, standard copyright notices, etc.",
    "), HTML and Javascript code.",
    "The texts were cleaned using the following preprocessing steps that are commonly applied to web pages:",
    "• The texts were tokenized into individual words and sentences using the NLTK package (Bird, 2006).",
    "• Sentences written in a language other than English were automatically detected and removed."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "• The texts were tokenized into individual words and sentences using the NLTK package (Bird, 2006)."
  ]
}